rows.label: tlk45350153_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Did you see the Divine Beast weapons
from Judicium?

rows.label: tlk45350153_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Apparently Senator Roderich was
researching them without permission.

rows.label: tlk45350153_02_msg0003
rows.name: I wish he'd asked me to help...

rows.label: tlk45350153_02_msg0004
rows.name:
Judicium may have fallen long ago,
but their technological prowess was
greater than Superbia's today!

rows.label: tlk45350153_02_msg0005
rows.name:
There are so many things we could
learn from their work.
